            "body": "Same issue is present with \"zt\" and \"zb\", and doesn't seem to be present in Vim because it has special logic in main.c for redrawing the cursorline. Adding `wp->w_valid &= ~VALID_VIRTCOL` to `scroll_cursor_top/bot/halfway` fixes the issue but may be unnecessarily costly.",
